### 10. Key Conventions & Architectural Patterns

| Aspect | Convention |
|--------|-----------|
| **Catalog** | `notification` (for notification & notification_setting tables) |
| **ID Strategy** | UUID-based `@GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")` |
| **Transaction** | `@Transactional` on write, `@Transactional(readOnly = true)` on read |
| **GraphQL Auth** | `@PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")` on all public endpoints |
| **User ID Injection** | `@UserId userId: String` in GraphQL Controllers |
| **Error Handling** | `CustomGraphQLException` for GraphQL errors, `Status` for gRPC |
| **Commit Messages** | `<type>/<ticket>: <description>` (e.g., `feat/#540: 프로모션 푸시알림`) |
| **Layer Separation** | No Repository access from GraphQL (gRPC Service required) |

